 />\n抵人quit莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40613fb90afdfaa16e5965dfe8b72ce60bf9af77","tid":84174,"uid":15302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"曾經我都咁諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家覺得quit先係正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2217f7e8face6d59a4a02a282255535b6b878e","tid":84174,"uid":40070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上莊咁戇鳩，早日quit早日回頭是岸</blockquote><br />\nAggar"},{"pid":"b0b67e7770947013c384d7e0abe33f433a1a81c1","tid":84174,"uid":62045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"掙扎咗好耐今日quit咗莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:睇住啲候選莊員諗tee定衛衣同諗咩色都傾咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲要有小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利利申：毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376dee857a6eca6a5fa5c32ecbcb84d96cc45b0e","tid":84174,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗十個有十一個上莊後都會後侮 <span style=\"color: red;\">尤其男仔</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwhy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b97449e5bdc889e932157503eb3def4b93bc566","tid":84174,"uid":38324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我諗十個有十一個上莊後都會後侮 <span style=\"color: red;\">尤其男仔</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwhy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif